She went to visit her in Macau, China.

189
00:09:46,744 --> 00:09:48,040
Inspector Ye, you're impressive.

190
00:09:48,270 --> 00:09:50,216
You managed to join
the Fire Inquiry Commission.

191
00:09:50,380 --> 00:09:51,400
Don't mention it.

192
00:09:51,550 --> 00:09:52,730
What matters is

193
00:09:52,790 --> 00:09:54,090
uncovering the truth quickly.

194
00:09:54,980 --> 00:09:56,392
How about we take a photo together?

195
00:09:56,408 --> 00:09:57,130
Sure. Let's do it.

196
00:10:00,780 --> 00:10:01,269
One more.

197
00:10:01,270 --> 00:10:02,850
Thank you so much.

198
