251
00:11:39,380 --> 00:11:40,520
Mai Zhihong.

252
00:11:43,340 --> 00:11:44,490
Have some fish.

253
00:11:44,620 --> 00:11:45,970
You're not eating anything.

254
00:11:46,500 --> 00:11:47,760
It's protein.

255
00:11:48,500 --> 00:11:49,149
Sir,

256
00:11:49,150 --> 00:11:50,280
beer, please.

257
00:11:50,310 --> 00:11:51,130
Okay.

258
00:12:12,070 --> 00:12:13,370
Mai Zhihong hides here.

259
00:12:13,432 --> 00:12:15,416
It's impossible
we can't find anything about him.

260
00:12:15,910 --> 00:12:17,040
Let's search one more time.

261
00:13:00,580 --> 00:13:01,370
Kaiqing.

262
00:13:19,652 --> 00:13:27,720
