263
00:13:42,830 --> 00:13:43,520
Bao,

264
00:13:44,860 --> 00:13:46,160
who beat you?

265
00:13:47,500 --> 00:13:48,800
I don't know.

266
00:13:49,380 --> 00:13:50,850
There were so many of them.

267
00:13:51,190 --> 00:13:53,000
I didn't dare look at them.

268
00:13:58,860 --> 00:14:00,130
Don't be afraid.

269
00:14:00,500 --> 00:14:01,520
Listen.

270
00:14:02,270 --> 00:14:03,099
You must remember

271
00:14:03,100 --> 00:14:04,850
the backs of each one of them.

272
00:14:04,980 --> 00:14:06,099
Like scanning photos,

273
00:14:06,100 --> 00:14:07,490
