274
00:14:07,740 --> 00:14:08,429
You're too young

275
00:14:08,430 --> 00:14:09,490
to fight them now.

276
00:14:09,550 --> 00:14:10,499
But when you grow up,

277
00:14:10,500 --> 00:14:11,789
track them down

278
00:14:11,790 --> 00:14:12,970
one by one

279
00:14:13,220 --> 00:14:14,920
